cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

This paper is about object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new sampling and learning strategy, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the importance of sample selection and its impact on the overall performance, which relates to natural language processing (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR) where sample selection is also an important aspect.
